column4: Hey Usain! I've heard you're the fastest man on Earth. How do you train to be so fast?
Hey Goku! I train hard every day, focusing on sprinting techniques and strength training. What about you? How do you get so fast?
Well, I do a lot of intense training too, but I also have a secret... Super Saiyan power! üí™
Wow, that's incredible! I wish I had that kind of power. What's it like to go beyond your limits like that?
It's amazing! The rush of energy is like nothing else. But it takes a lot of discipline and control.
I can imagine. Pushing my own limits on the track feels similar, I guess. Any tips for improving speed?
Stay focused, keep pushing your limits, and never give up! Also, a balanced diet and proper rest are crucial.
Thanks, Goku! I'll keep that in mind. Maybe one day I can run as fast as you fly.
You're already amazing, Usain! Just keep up the great work and who knows? Maybe you'll reach Super Saiyan speed! üí™
Haha, I'd love that! Thanks for the chat, Goku. Keep saving the world!
Anytime, Usain! Keep breaking those records! üèÖ
Goku, have you ever raced against anyone on Earth?
Not really. Most people can't keep up with me. But I've raced against other Saiyans and even some aliens! üëΩ
That sounds intense! Do you think I could keep up with you if I trained as hard as you?
With your determination, you could get pretty close! But Super Saiyan speed is on another level.
Well, I'll keep pushing my limits then. Maybe one day we can have a friendly race.
That would be fun! I'd love to see how fast you can go.
By the way, have you ever had to use your speed to save someone?
Many times! Speed is crucial in battles and rescues. It's saved my friends and the world more than once.
That's amazing. I use my speed to inspire others, but you've literally saved lives.
Inspiration is just as important, Usain. You motivate people to be their best selves.
Thanks, Goku. That means a lot coming from a hero like you.
You're welcome! So, what are your goals for the future?
I want to keep pushing the limits of human speed and maybe explore new sports. How about you?
I want to keep training, protect Earth, and get stronger. There's always a new challenge!
That's the spirit! Always striving for more.
Hey, nice photo! Where was that taken?
That was on Planet Namek. Beautiful place, but it had its share of dangers.
Wow, I'd love to see it someday. If only I could travel through space like you.
Maybe someday you will! The universe is full of surprises.
Goku, do you ever get scared before a big fight?
Sometimes, but I use that fear to fuel my determination. It's what keeps me going.
I feel the same way before a big race. That adrenaline rush is something else.
Exactly! It's what makes us push our limits.
Do you ever relax, Goku? Or is it all training and fighting?
I do relax! I love spending time with my family and eating good food. üçú
Same here! Nothing beats a good meal after a hard day's work.
Absolutely! Maybe we can share a meal someday.
I'd love that, Goku! Let's make it happen.
It's a date! Until then, keep being awesome, Usain.
You too, Goku. Take care! üëãüèª
Bye!
